  <evidence rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">II Sharing of information We may share your PII and non-personal information including your name address email address and any transactions you conduct on our website or offline with us with a third party advertising partner and its service providers in order to deliver tailored advertising to you that match your interests when you visit our website as well as other websites Our advertising partner will make the data that we provide anonymous so that no one else will receive your PII</evidence>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

